707
00:40:38,372 --> 00:40:49,570
Rym: It's hard to compare any PAX because the first PAX I went to was in many ways the best one I went to, but it was mostly because I'd never experienced a fan convention that good before.

708
00:40:50,350 --> 00:40:52,470
Rym: I mean, I went into it before that PAX.

709
00:40:52,530 --> 00:41:06,830
