710
00:41:07,651 --> 00:41:14,950
Scott: So it was much more intimate in its size, like going to see a concert, literally, where there's less people at the concert.

711
00:41:15,370 --> 00:41:17,930
Scott: You get this more intimate setting than when you go to the stadium concert.

712
00:41:18,090 --> 00:41:33,370
